  "overview": {
    "description": "Microsoft Foundry is a comprehensive Azure-based platform for building, deploying, and managing AI applications and agents at scale. It provides integrated tools for creating generative AI applications, managing models, monitoring performance, and implementing trustworthy AI practices.",
    "purpose": "Enable developers and teams to build production-grade AI applications with enterprise-grade governance, monitoring, and safety features."
  },
